originalText.text: Dr. Carrasco is the best ObGYN I have ever been to. He is so personable, smart and professional. He truly cares and looks out for his patients best interest, on top of that he is hilarious! He puts me at ease with his jokes and health advice. He always responds to my concerns and many messages. He is one of a kind :)

originalText.text:
Inelda O'Keeffe
I have been a patient of Dr. Carrasco for approximately twenty years. He is a very professional, knowledgeable, understanding, and empathetic doctor who cares for the needs of his patients. He is a doctor who is willing to go the extra mile in order to help and support his patients.  He is always eager to get to know and address the needs of his patients. When I go for a checkup with Dr. Carrasco, I feel at home.  I wish more doctors could be like Dr. Carrasco; that way this world would be a better and more pleasant place.  I would give Dr. Carrasco not five stars, but all the stars in the sky. He is simply the best doctor.

originalText.text: This is the worst doctors experience Iâ€™ve ever had. I went last year but just received my 4th bill from them all because they keep typing in my insurance number incorrectly, even after I call them to correct it. Not to mention that Dr. Carrasco was incredibly belittling in our 5 minute appointment (after I waited almost an hour), did not listen to my concerns, and did not properly check me for the PCOS symptoms I described. He made me feel like I was being dramatic about worrying that I had PCOS and talked to me like a child. I finally saw a female OBGYN this year, was listened to fully, properly tested, and then officially diagnosed with PCOS so that I can now properly address my health concerns. I would not recommend coming here.
